Usage: set_dynamic_power_simulation [-help] [-activity_pattern <string>]
                                    [-period <string>] [-reset]
                                    [-resolution <string>]

-help                          # Prints out the command usage
-activity_pattern <string>     # jitter activity pattern (string, optional)
-period <string>               # Specifies the simulation period that dynamic
                               # power analysis will use. (string, optional)
-reset                         # Resets all specified options back to default
                               # values. (bool, optional)
-resolution <string>           # Specifies the transient time step size or
                               # resolution. Default: ps (picosecond),
                               # (string, optional)